name: supabase-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for using Supabase in Next.js applications
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx}

- Use Prisma to handle schema, migrations, and queries for Supabase.
- Implement server-side actions for database operations to enhance security.
- Cache database results in actions and use real-time subscriptions for updates.
- Use `@supabase/ssr` for server-side rendering compatibility.
- Implement proper error handling and validation for database operations.